data.description: Live near Lake Conroe in this newer home. Built in 2018. Spacious one story house with 4 bedrooms, 2 baths and 2 car garage. Lake Conroe access. Home was repainted, carpet replaced. Open concept, traditional home with plenty of room in all 4 bedrooms. Small shed and extra paved outdoor space in rear yard
